snippet.title: [Official Trailer] The Diary | Narrative Puzzle Game
snippet.description:
The Diary is a 2D suspenseful narrative puzzle game that revolves around several distinct "diaries," including a journal full of life but full of doubts, two investigative notebooks written by different people, and the planner's diary, which will all be displayed before you. 
Add to your wishlist!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2343880/_/
Discord: N5B44cezHm
